{"tid":381133,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"我放了380天假—悉尼• 紐西蘭南島","createTime":"2017-08-30T16:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T17:15:04.000Z","uid":141782,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d37a5f3cd85b7a4b68d92f5c299c0cfa67a9374","tid":381133,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"Grad咗之後本身諗住讀postgrad，點知on99搞錯d 野，搞搞下遲成三個sem先開到學。就係咁樣，我由舊年五月開始就無啦啦變咗雙失， 意想唔到多咗個gap year，亦都去咗唔少地方。趁我仲記得想記低今年做過d 咩。<br />\n<br />\n呢篇會講悉尼+紐西蘭南島。紐西蘭南島去咗: <br />\nChristchurch &rarr; Kaikoura &rarr;Picton &rarr; Nelson &rarr; Abel Tasman &rarr; Westport &rarr; Franz Josef &rarr; Wanaka &rarr;Queenstown &rarr; Glenorchy &rarr;Mt Cook &rarr;Tekapo<br />\n<br />\n最初我係喺Sydney做intern，諗住做完之後去個簡單grad trip就返歸。Intern尾聲嗰陣，收到學校信又呢又路，因為太麻煩決定乜都唔理行開下先。喺Sydney最後去咗La perouse，亦都係我成個Grad Trip既開始。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/234521_2e9616cfcd4ee24d4263af495cacc5a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F234521_2e9616cfcd4ee24d4263af495cacc5a0.jpg&h=2b7957f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到La perouse，唔會係咩大景，就係有塊好大既草地連住個島，島上面好多一個個窿嗰d 石（唔知點稱呼佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。我心諗：唔係掛講到咁靚。諗住坐低hea下算既時候，突然間聽到有把女聲講廣東話大叫：嗰度有呀！然之後拎住部電話係咁走，一轉頭見竟然見到我個friend 黎到呢頭捉精靈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我本能反應走都走唔切，就沿住舊石爬落海邊。頂原來下面咁鬼靚，不過真係小心d 海浪好大，影影下一個浪打埋黎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/234700_922e8b893aca90ed39a2926832372327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F234700_922e8b893aca90ed39a2926832372327.jpg&h=f6337210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/235855_d5decdd3e452efedaca6ea25d1e03e81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F235855_d5decdd3e452efedaca6ea25d1e03e81.jpg&h=be22b57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有石就爬見到好多新人影相<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/234959_e8df8db2797ed6631109408b09503641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F234959_e8df8db2797ed6631109408b09503641.jpg&h=67e202f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後成身泥上返黎， 買咗fish and chips，學下澳洲人hea下hea下又一日。一擺低就瀨晒野，幾十隻海鷗圍住晒搶9晒我d野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/235455_62504b8c1dcba5ae8fead7793b5e83f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F235455_62504b8c1dcba5ae8fead7793b5e83f9.jpg&h=e39ca25a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n望下個日曆好快intern就完都唔知返唔返香港好，因為我咩都冇plan。我就諗橫掂返香港都係冇野做，不如去個長少少既旅行。於是我上去就book咗去Christchurch 既機票。<br />\n<br />\n(我有做某網上雜誌有出過文，所以可能會有人認得d 相，認得既懇求你切勿相認，唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾張南島既相亂入，因為我覺得最靚既景都喺呢度但有排未去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/000512_b4dbdd41f218f9c44a8882c096969476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F000512_b4dbdd41f218f9c44a8882c096969476.jpg&h=302f2932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/000724_20f4c6169bab6852e7761cd1e626b17c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F000724_20f4c6169bab6852e7761cd1e626b17c.jpg&h=5142c742&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccf8a5d2dc2e4c67108cf7e1f775887b5acad9de","tid":381133,"uid":106165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:15:17.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n黎緊可能去奧克蘭旅行"},{"pid":"9bb774776f0470daf3a1e26a038a782a64727885","tid":381133,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:31:17.000Z","msg":"我訂咗hop-on hop-off bus環島咁玩，因為一條友渣車真係玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 悉尼飛去紐西蘭南島，喺飛機上面已經見到望唔到盡頭既雪山。去到Christchurch司機接我去Kaikoura，紐西蘭人d 寓工作於娛樂既態度真係。個叫Leftie既司機一路揸車一路響鞍，之後車上面既其他鬼仔鬼妹係咁係度9叫，長期索咗K咁款。我心諗有冇咁high 呀，跟住去咗Kaikoura。（呢part同picton我會飛咗佢因為我都唔記得做過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係記得悶到嘔）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到Abel Tasman，睇網上人地講如果天氣好會好靚，不過我去到嗰日又凍天又黑，本身普普通同既山景變得更加唔靚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/002240_5f64b3f38aea7966ac927b022c434620.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F002240_5f64b3f38aea7966ac927b022c434620.jpg&h=630d0a4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一朝早冇野做，就一條友走左去行山，紐西蘭真係吸啖氣都清新d。一路行都係呢d 綠色成條隧道咁，行下行下已經成粒鐘都仲係咁，突然間有d 聲好似有人咁，越望越似鬼片於是我好驚咁跑住走。走到一半見到個鬼妹fd，又捉返我陪佢行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/002943_c879791477f1f7a179b0e461c8d6507c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F002943_c879791477f1f7a179b0e461c8d6507c.png&h=e7c52786&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e718f1ce2efc11b76ac192bcbe9632a98691fb3c","tid":381133,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:56:52.000Z","msg":"唔記得講南島我去咗廿二日"},{"pid":"0031d369ab8b91e6d64cdfa918543bdfaea66fab","tid":381133,"uid":141782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:22:22.000Z","msg":"終於捱完個好悶既Abel Tasman，去咗個更悶既Westport。<br />\n<br />\n而喺Westport我竟然留咗三日，原因係去Franz Josef 既巴士full 晒。臨落車嗰陣個司機講Westport d 路好簡單，就係得兩條大街，冇可能蕩失路架啦。最後我真係蕩失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （條條街都一樣樣其實好難分），不過紐西蘭人真係好好，見我on99咁樣就問我係咪蕩失路教我出返大街。<br />\n<br />\n睇返d 路真係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/012159_6801046d42590c2d220d111e4352be5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F012159_6801046d42590c2d220d111e4352be5d.png&h=d4f3cc30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWestport係以前產煤既鎮，總之真係咩都冇。呢三日，我完全漫無目的咁9下9下，朝早就去同cafe 既店員吹水，之後行到去碼頭又同漁民吹水。雖然當時覺得呢三日好無謂，依家諗返起可以周街傾計感覺好正好似多咗好多fd 咁。<br />\n<br />\n得閒到唔係撚狗就撚貓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011836_3db4563ec58fb1ed2ba359127576a10d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011836_3db4563ec58fb1ed2ba359127576a10d.jpg&h=cfb64dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011946_36a756f2b139a11071dae5bd3b428e33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011946_36a756f2b139a11071dae5bd3b428e33.jpg&h=bc3fbbc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/012057_5a7a324b6520dccabaca50f959a8a2e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F012057_5a7a324b6520dccabaca50f959a8a2e8.jpg&h=861fce76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3aa919471ccb8a42b510b0eddfba731acafcd076","tid":381133,"uid":61355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:44:50.000Z","msg":"玩咁多個地方 <br />\n覺得邊到最正"},{"pid":"4f264ec8a4aeb12231f2edbc31bf40d44afa50cf","tid":381133,"uid":31920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:46:01.000Z","msg":"有錢真好"},{"pid":"bc58bd119e8a20163e7b8a7bb6d3641fa7949b9c","tid":381133,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:48:26.000Z","msg":"去Westport途中既lookout<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/014209_2b371c2f42ea098579c8bf5cf5162d1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F014209_2b371c2f42ea098579c8bf5cf5162d1a.jpg&h=90fbe742&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭嗰段旅程我都係靠住明天會更好呢個信念支撐，跟住終於等到intercity去Punakaiki睇Pancake rocks。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle睇既相係咁<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.punakaiki.co.nz/wp-content/themes/punakaiki-responsive/images/punakaiki-header02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.punakaiki.co.nz%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fpunakaiki-responsive%2Fimages%2Fpunakaiki-header02.jpg&h=7a5d584c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我去到係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/014517_1564323396caa80bcb1471293044512c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F014517_1564323396caa80bcb1471293044512c.jpg&h=f36e9850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半粒鐘就行晒亦冇想像中咁宏偉。<br />\n<br />\n朝早去到要晏晝先有車返去，我沿住條山路一路行去海邊（其實我都唔知行緊去邊），我諗行咗幾粒鐘啦，無啦啦做咗徒步JJ。行到去海邊仲有隻好撚惡幾金毛尋回追住吠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/014627_c47339f3c9ab34836f3ecf0e2ec52d9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F014627_c47339f3c9ab34836f3ecf0e2ec52d9e.jpg&h=050a78d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/014705_109deb73fae94af66210b562362240b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F014705_109deb73fae94af66210b562362240b9.jpg&h=f556b473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我覺得一條友行喺一條無人既公路真係好浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dad88d460d1497cb2952edf7f2c0d5611f66bc8","tid":381133,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"00ab11aaf3110e60b7b000e3984ec1c1284317bd","tid":381133,"uid":29469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T19:20:22.000Z","msg":"想當年去澳洲working hoilday 2年，順便去埋紐西蘭南島。。睇番你d 相回憶又番曬黎"},{"pid":"d379bc0ebd1cb109ee7b656e233c01050505abee","tid":381133,"uid":44699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"留名 11月去南島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858402dfa4d7c9cf321aa9e1cdd0a66e1c1973c8","tid":381133,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:32:29.000Z","msg":"相好靚"},{"pid":"ba5e0a74b18915e9bb18e13c8aa2513c3b3e43d9","tid":381133,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"有個同車既菲律賓肥婆（佢個名叫Princess<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）係咁擒高擒低拉住我幫佢影相，頂我影咗成十幾張都唔ok，搞搞下都成十分鐘，跟住有隻鬼行完落黎問我地做咩唔上山，山上面靚咁多。我聽到十五分鐘內狗衝上山。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肥婆本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/120902_d2f6a945aec922fdaab03590a4b0e5f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F120902_d2f6a945aec922fdaab03590a4b0e5f6.jpg&h=1288b555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山上面真係好靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/121313_67b3352e37cc51925e202d9084860727.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F121313_67b3352e37cc51925e202d9084860727.jpg&h=5edb0c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/121500_7b1d893791ba3af900288c8811580cd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F121500_7b1d893791ba3af900288c8811580cd4.jpg&h=9316b35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/121547_b301f864e2f73a510ed8e62ba7aa331d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F121547_b301f864e2f73a510ed8e62ba7aa331d.jpg&h=e0fc8b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過咗好耐個個開始落返山，突然見到肥婆喘晒起咁上黎，然後9叫我未睇seal呀！等埋我呀！<br />\n有個鬼妹開口話唔洗上啦乜都冇，跟住肥婆仲話好睬佢行咗一半唔洗嘥咁多力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c747d893f324cb1eeb16674af019a081451c279","tid":381133,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"下一站Franz Josef <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/122308_532ef81b8bf62910f993e22f18ef7272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F122308_532ef81b8bf62910f993e22f18ef7272.jpg&h=1b700df7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cf193b9038a2043bb8cd3063410acbb11e1373b","tid":381133,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩咁多個地方 <br />\n覺得邊到最正</blockquote><br />\nfranz josef 之後嗰d 都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5221a50373d7dc297ed543a410a268a820bd36f8","tid":381133,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"屋企人有錢真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585b01e533d136bd1610aab9f18d5b1016d44cdf","tid":381133,"uid":71502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"玩兩年"},{"pid":"d57d48f36bd89bbb7de6605c8bdb90fc42cb4b93","tid":381133,"uid":66922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:03:15.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4556f2b8c5d0686f4428914b1013bf9447b8cef9","tid":381133,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企人有錢真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我中間有影event 幫補下既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaed44d2c124a888f83ee7befbd556ae38587399","tid":381133,"uid":61970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}